fields.description:
It would be good to have additional controls over the request access functionality, such as:
 * Which admin would be notified about them;
 * A custom e-mail address to receive the notifications (this can be useful to keep track of the requests apart from the Instance - for log keeping purposes).

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Cloud*. Using *JIRA Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRASERVER-47611].
  {panel}

Customer want to create products that aggregates billing information for organisations. As part of this, they want to be able to pull Atlassian billing information out of your REST API that is akin to the billing information that is on Atlassian Billing page.

At the moment there's any workaround functions to substitute this feature.
